&lt;li&gt;Prepare and process expense reports in a timely and accurate manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support meeting preparation by gathering materials, creating agendas, preparing presentations, and organizing follow-up items.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and help manage executive inboxes as needed, including drafting responses, flagging priorities, and tracking action items.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted liaison between executives and internal or external stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle sensitive and confidential information with professionalism and discretion.&lt;/li&gt;
